 ed="R042" n="0155a09"/><div type='w' level='4'><head>第十九章</head><lb
 ed="X" n="0992c22"/><lb
 ed="R042" n="0155a10"/><ab type="verse">森羅殿上鬼多般百沸油鐺萬刃山　　<lb
